&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Internship Opportunity at Xebia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt; 3 months to start with.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type:&lt;/strong&gt; Internship (Full-time / Part-time)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Atlanta, GA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Xebia&lt;/strong&gt;, we are passionate about shaping the next generation of technology and consulting leaders. As part of our continued investment in early-career talent, we are excited to offer &lt;strong&gt;Internship opportunities&lt;/strong&gt; for motivated and curious individuals who want real-world exposure and hands-on experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are ?&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With over 20 years of experience, our global network of passionate technologists and pioneering craftsmen deliver cutting-edge technology and game-changing consulting to companies on the brink of transformation. Since 2001, we have grown from a Java company into a full-service digital consulting company with 4500+ professionals working on a worldwide ambition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are organized in complementary chapters – teams with a tremendous amount of knowledge and experience within a particular field, such as Agile, DevOps, Data and AI, Cloud, Software Technology, Functional Programming, Low Code, and Microsoft.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We help the world’s top 250 companies and category leaders overcome digital challenges, embrace innovation, adopt new technology, and implement new business models. In addition to high-quality consulting, we also provide offshoring and nearshoring services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more details please visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;a id=&quot;menur1v2r&quot; class=&quot;fui-Link ___1q1shib f2hkw1w f3rmtva f1ewtqcl fyind8e f1k6fduh f1w7gpdv fk6fouc fjoy568 figsok6 f1s184ao f1mk8lai fnbmjn9 f1o700av f13mvf36 f1cmlufx f9n3di6 f1ids18y f1tx3yz7 f1deo86v f1eh06m1 f1iescvh fhgqx19 f1olyrje f1p93eir f1nev41a f1h8hb77 f1lqvz6u f10aw75t fsle3fq f17ae5zn&quot; href=&quot;http://www.xebia.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;www.xebia.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Work closely with experienced professionals on real client and internal projects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Assist in research, analysis, documentation, and delivery activities relevant to your domain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Learn industry best practices, tools, and frameworks used in a global consulting environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams in an agile, fast-paced setting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Gain mentorship and continuous feedback throughout your internship journey&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Students or recent graduates in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Engineering, Computer Science, IT.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Strong analytical, communication, and problem-solving skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A proactive mindset with a willingness to learn and take ownership&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Ability to work independently as well as collaboratively&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with Modern Coding languages and AI&amp;nbsp;is a plus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Gain&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Hands-on experience with real-world projects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Exposure to cutting-edge technologies and modern delivery practices&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Mentorship from industry experts and leaders&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A collaborative, inclusive, and learning-driven culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Potential opportunity for future full-time roles based on performance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
